HEADWORD: Denouncer
<hw>De*noun"cer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who denounces,
or declares, as a menace.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Here comes the sad <qex>denouncer</qex> of my fate.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dense</ent>⟦br⟧
